Robert Parrish https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robert_Parrish 0 Robert R. Parrish (January 4, 1916 – December 4, 1995) was an American film director, editor, writer, and child actor. He received an Academy Award for Film Editing for his contribution to Body and Soul (1947).
